data.description: East Ridge located. Home located in the cul-de-sac of Jordan Run. Convenient to I-75, shopping and Camp Jordan part and more. Open floor plan with Cathedral Ceiling, tile floors, hardwood . Master on the main with walk -in closet and full bath. 2 bedrooms upstairs with Jack & Jill full bath. Large kitchen area with concrete counter tops and good cabinet space, laundry closet, half bath and fireplace. Screened porch with private fenced back yard. Full 2 car garage/basement with good storage and work bench and shelf.
